A wintumber tree planted in a player-owned house.

A wintumber tree is a holiday item that can be planted in a player-owned house. It can be obtained by completing one of the Christmas holiday events that occur once per year. This also rewards the player with all other holiday items associated with Christmas. The tree is untradeable and may be planted on any free non-hotspot space in the Garden or on any free outdoor space of a player-owned house. If lost or destroyed, the player can obtain another from Diango in Draynor Village.

Before the 2013 Christmas event, it could only be obtained from picking one up from various spawn points around the world during 5–12 August.

Trivia[edit | edit source]

  • The tree is similar to a Christmas tree, donned with garlands and constantly glittering.

A '''wintumber tree''' is a holiday item that can be planted in a [[player-owned house]]. It can be obtained by completing one of the [[Christmas event|Christmas]] [[holiday events]] that occur once per year. This also rewards the player with all other holiday items associated with Christmas. The tree is untradeable and may be planted on any free non-hotspot space in the [[Garden]] or on any free outdoor space of a player-owned house. If lost or destroyed, the player can obtain another from [[Diango]] in [[Draynor Village]].

Before the [[2013 Christmas event]], it could only be obtained from picking one up from various spawn points around the world during 5–12 August.

==Trivia==
*The tree is similar to a Christmas tree, donned with garlands and constantly glittering.
